    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "NOTE: (1) First replace at 90,000 km (54,000 miles), then every 60,000 km (36,000 miles).",
      "style": "note"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "(2) Periodic maintenance is not required for CG engine models. However, if valve noise increases, check valve clearance.",
      "style": "note"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "(3) Perform only according to \"Maintenance under severe driving conditions\".",
      "style": "note"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "* Maintenance items with \"*\" should be performed more frequently according to \"Maintenance under severe driving conditions\".",
      "style": "note"
